Package: entropies
Type: Package
Title: Plotting ternary entropy diagrams for joint distributions, contingency matrices, etc.
Version: 0.9.1
Date: 2015-02-23
Author: F.J. Valverde-Albacete
Maintainer: F.J. Valverde-Albacete <franciscojvalverde@gmail.com>
Imports: entropy, ggtern
Description: Uses the ggtern and entropy packages to plot ternary entropy diagrams whether in the split form or not.
